5.3 Policy Management UI

The UI simplifies significantly with single-decision policies:

Remove the rules section (expandable cards, add rule button)

decision becomes a top-level toggle (ALLOW/DENY)

match conditions as grouped inputs by dimension

unless conditions as a repeatable typed list

